机打撒科技大\n","images":[],"time":"2023-10-13T11:49:27.000+00:00","uid":1,"email":"3061588683@qq.com","username":"test","avatar":"","like":0,"collect":0},{"id":9,"type":2,"title":"测试我是测试帖子","text":"测试一下缓存是否生效\n","images":[],"time":"2023-10-13T11:35:43.000+00:00","uid":1,"email":"3061588683@qq.com","username":"test","avatar":"","like":0,"collect":0},{"id":8,"type":5,"title":"千万别在咸鱼上到手刀","text":"太坑了\n","images":[],"time":"2023-10-13T11:34:26.000+00:00","uid":1,"email":"3061588683@qq.com","username":"test","avatar":"","like":0,"collect":0},{"id":6,"type":3,"title":"论坛出现超大BUG赶紧修","text":"为什么不能直接给我匹配一个女友，要同城的，最好同学校\n","images":[],"time":"2023-10-13T10:28:30.000+00:00","uid":1,"email":"3061588683@qq.com","username":"test","avatar":"","like":0,"collect":0}],"message":"请求成功"}
